Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射装置 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引力子放射线
