Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命中地点 放射线轨道轴半径100千单位内的所有物质已消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威力强劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 比预计的还要高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试验结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴美 切断希格斯粒子的供给
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴美 出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希格斯粒子的通道无法切断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射装置不接受发出的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在不断从供给源中吸取希格斯粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
